expression.expression:
CASE
  WHEN LENGTH(imtday) = 6 THEN to_timestamp(
    CONCAT(
      DATE_ADD(
        CAST(SUBSTRING(IMUPMJ + 1900000, 1, 4) AS DATE),
        CAST(SUBSTRING(IMUPMJ, 4, 3) AS INT) -1
      ),
      """",
      imtday
    ),
    'yyyy-MM-ddHHmmss'
  )
  WHEN LENGTH(imtday) = 5 THEN to_timestamp(
    CONCAT(
      DATE_ADD(
        CAST(SUBSTRING(IMUPMJ + 1900000, 1, 4) AS DATE),
        CAST(SUBSTRING(IMUPMJ, 4, 3) AS INT) -1
      ),
      """",
      concat(0, imtday)
    ),
    'yyyy-MM-ddHHmmss'
  )
  ELSE to_timestamp(
    date_add(
      cast(substring(IMUPMJ + 1900000, 1, 4) AS Date),
      cast(substring(IMUPMJ, 4, 3) as int) -1
    )
  )
END
